    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1900-08-19T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1900-08-19T00:00:00-05:00" n="280"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d280">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Adee</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Goodnow</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1900-08-19">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 19, 1900</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Two telegrams relative inquiry Nankin viceroys received. You will assure them
                    that announced policy of this Government rests on consideration for the Chinese
                    people not implicated in antiforeign <pb facs="0364" n="266" xml:id="pg_266"/>
                    outrages, and will duly regard high personalities of Empress and Emperor. In
                    circular of July 3 to powers we said: <quote rend="blockquote">
                        <p>The policy of the United States is to seek a solution which may bring
                            about permanent peace and safety to China and to preserve Chinese
                            territorial and administrative entity.</p>
                    </quote>
                </p>
                <p>To this we adhere.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee</hi>, <hi rend="italic">Acting.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
